<title>USA: Harbinger sees Q1 charge from acquisition. [corrected 15:43 gmt]</title>
<headline>Harbinger sees Q1 charge from acquisition. [corrected 15:43 gmt]</headline>
<dateline>ATLANTA 1996-10-28</dateline>
<text>
<p>Harbinger Corp said Monday that it expects a first quarter 1997 charge of between $6 million and $7.5 million as a result of the acquisition of the 30 percent interest it does not already own in Harbinger NET Services LLC.</p>
<p>The company said in a release Monday that it will purchase the remaining 30 percent equity interest in Harbinger NET from BellSouth Corp for about $7.2 million in cash and stock.</p>
<p>(Corrects to read &quot;...$7.2 million in cash and stock&quot; instead of &quot;...$7.2 million in cash.&quot;)</p>
